(77, 1, '2016-02-07 06:04:22', '2016-02-07 06:04:22', '<p>Chicken Ati-atihan, the branch located in Purok-13 Hagkol, Valencia , Bukidnon , is owned  and Managed  by Ms.  Babes Gangga Peduche, together with her is  Rechel R. Genovia, the Supervisor of the restaurant, and 14 other staff personnel. Last  August 20, 2012, they buy this branch and  that is why they are not franchising it anymore. Valencia Chicken Ati-atihan Branch celebrate their 9th years  anniversary in business last October 29, 2015.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<h3 style="\r\n    font-size: 18px;\r\n    font-weight: 800;">We are here.</h3>\r\n<div id="branch-location">\r\n [mapsmarker marker="1"]\r\n</div>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nChicken Ati-atihan offers us a different types and package of catering, Their package pricing is usually applied in the premise for occasion such as Birthdays, Conference, Wedding and etc. They usually using banquet service and Buffet service during the off-premise catering, depends on the Set of Package that the customer will choose.</p>\r\n<p>Sasayaw ka sa sarap! That is how they describe when you have already tried to dine at Chicken Ati-atihan in Valencia City. The slogan proudly declares “sasayaw ka sa sarap” or “so delicious, it will make you dance”. </p>\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'Chicken Ati-atihan Valencia Branch', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about-content', '', '', '2016-02-23 14:43:33', '2016-02-23 14:43:33', '', 0, 'http://chickenatiatihan.local/?p=77', 0, 'post', '', 0),
