(111, 1, '2016-02-23 15:02:24', '2016-02-23 15:02:24', 'Chicken Ati-atihan is a fast-food restaurant that provides Filipino food and Filipino style chicken barbeque. It was first conceptualized in the year 2003 by Mr. Aries Christopher Alvarez, a veteran medical sales representative from Abbott Pharmaceuticals. Mr. Alvarez before was managing a restaurant owned by his aunt in Roxas City when some disagreements between them led him to resign and to start his own carinderia business in Capiz.\r\n\r\nThe name Chicken Ati-atihan was coined when Mr. Alvarez witnessed the spectacular festival in Kalibo, Aklan; the concept was used for their carenderia business. He personally travels around the country to check on his franchises and making sure that the quality is maintained in order to meet the satisfaction of his customers. Today it has more than 50 franchise outlets nationwide, a testament to his success.\r\n\r\nChicken Ati-Atihan ranks among the fastest franchise chain in the Visayas and Mindanao regions. To provide an affordable authentic Filipino taste of our chicken and array of food found in the menu. Even when circumstances grip the people’s expenditure, Chicken Ati-Atihan is one flexible and exceptional dining restaurant that understands the people’s needs. Taken at very affordable rates, the ordinary men in the streets can always dine and enjoy a festive meal. Being known for Pagkaing Sulit. The consistency of every recipe cooked is attributed to the sauce taken from the finest herbs that is used for marinating the food. That’s why Chicken Ati-Atihan is so unique, and authentic.', 'What We Are.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'what-we-are', '', '', '2016-02-23 15:14:13', '2016-02-23 15:14:13', '', 0, 'http://chickenatiatihan.local/?p=111', 0, 'post', '', 0),
